root: ^Thank you Hanae, for all you've done.
^It was my pleasure to help, I wish you luck with you and Kat.
^That means a lot Hanae, I will try my best. Hopefully my feelings get across to her.
^Uuuhhh, Hanae, can you give us a little room, kinda want to do this in private...
^O-oh, my bad, I'll get going then!
^(What a strange girl, willing to help a nobody like me. Alright here it goes...)
